| Variant / CVA compliance rows | `docs/reference/ui/UI_AUDIT.md` |
| Verification / sandbox | `docs/operations/TESTING.md` |
| Monorepo `pnpm` scripts / sync | `docs/operations/SCRIPTS.md` |
| Release / publish contract | `docs/operations/DEPLOY.md` |
| Backlog / BO / M-phases | `docs/REVIEW_TODO.md`, `docs/ROADMAP.md` |
| System shape (hub only) | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` |

## AGENTS.md and rules

- **AGENTS.md** — routing and guardrails only; no full domain rule copies.
- **`.cursor/rules/`** — Cursor editing behavior; not architecture contracts.
- **`.agents/skills/`** — multi-step verification procedures.
